**Home loan EMI** is the fixed monthly payment you make to repay your housing loan. It covers both the interest component and the principal repayment. In the early years, the EMI is mostly interest; as the loan progresses, more goes toward principal. This calculator shows your EMI, total interest payable, and a full year-by-year amortization schedule.
